Champion of Brell <br></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#414141><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub13.ezboard.com/utwiggietymberwolf.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Twiggie Tymberwolf</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Adventurer of Underfoot <img src=http://www.brellserilis.net/images/goldstartr.gif align=middle></span><br>  Posts: 1131<br> <font color=#CC9900>(6/13/01 1:59:24 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: Terror is a Piece of Cake....</span><hr size=1> Come on Nillon, be nice,  she's trying to learn how to kill him with the normal armor raid crew that they have.  This means level 46-55 players.   A normal armor mob raid can take down all three golems.  I've been on Harpers raids where they did it.<br>
<br>
Yes he can be killed by a normal SR raid without any buffs up, I've been there for those too.  But Violent Harvest and many others can't do that.  She's trying to ask advice so she can go do it with the crew they have.  She's doing exactly what you and many others have told people to do, just go do it. They did and they failed after getting him over half way down. She's not asking to be hand held all the way through it, just asking some advice on how to improve what they did.  They already had the right ideas but just needed a few more tips. <p><table>
